01:16:11,568 --> 01:16:12,533
And the soul-heart?

1396
01:16:16,673 --> 01:16:18,640
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1397
01:16:24,681 --> 01:16:25,613
[GRUNTS]

1398
01:16:25,649 --> 01:16:28,616
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1399
01:16:28,652 --> 01:16:31,619
[CLANKING]

1400
01:16:31,655 --> 01:16:34,255
[GRUNTS]

1401
01:16:44,601 --> 01:16:46,267
Magearna, we're here.

1402
01:16:51,308 --> 01:16:53,508
[ALL GASP]

1403
01:16:53,543 --> 01:16:57,278
MEOWTH: It's heart
is still broken.

1404
01:16:57,314 --> 01:16:59,447
Sure it can move
and all that stuff.

1405
01:16:59,482 --> 01:17:06,421
But now, Magearna's voice,
I can't hear it at all.

1406
01:17:06,456 --> 01:17:08,423
[GRUNTS]

1407
01:17:10,660 --> 01:17:12,427
[ALL SIGH]

1408
01:17:12,495 --> 01:17:13,428
[CLANKING]

1409
01:17:13,463 --> 01:17:14,228
[ALL GASPING]

1410
01:17:20,437 --> 01:17:21,436
Oh, no.

1411
01:17:21,471 --> 01:17:26,107
The fortress is set to
fall onto Nebel Plateau.

1412
01:17:26,142 --> 01:17:27,342
Can it be stopped?

1413
01:17:27,377 --> 01:17:30,411
It can't it looks like
the control system is out.

1414
01:17:30,447 --> 01:17:34,048
All because of Alva.

1415
01:17:34,084 --> 01:17:36,084
And even if we were
able to escape--

1416
01:17:48,498 --> 01:17:51,065
Isn't there any way at all?

1417
01:17:51,101 --> 01:17:52,467
We can't change course.

1418
01:17:52,502 --> 01:17:55,002
The only way would be
to explode the fortress

1419
01:17:55,038 --> 01:17:57,405
into a pile of dust.

1420
01:17:57,440 --> 01:18:01,109
Explosions are my specialty.

1421
01:18:01,144 --> 01:18:02,276
Hold on.

1422
01:18:02,312 --> 01:18:03,144
You're out of water.

1423
01:18:06,349 --> 01:18:11,285
Part of the fortress runs on
steam so it has water tanks.

1424
01:18:11,321 --> 01:18:13,988
Volcanion, I'll take you there.

1425
01:18:14,023 --> 01:18:15,990
Please do.

1426
01:18:16,025 --> 01:18:19,060
Everybody, wait on my
sister's flying machine.

1427
01:18:19,095 --> 01:18:20,328
I'm going with you.

1428
01:18:20,363 --> 01:18:21,329
Pika ka.

1429
01:18:27,070 --> 01:18:28,035
Over here!

1430
01:18:31,174 --> 01:18:32,974
I can smell water.

1431
01:18:35,412 --> 01:18:37,345
[GROANING]

1432
01:18:39,048 --> 01:18:42,016
This thing is really stuck.

1433
01:18:42,051 --> 01:18:43,050
I've got it.

1434
01:18:43,086 --> 01:18:44,452
Go for it, Pikachu.

1435
01:18:44,487 --> 01:18:45,420
Irontail!

1436
01:18:45,455 --> 01:18:47,054
Pika!

1437
01:18:47,090 --> 01:18:48,289
Ah, pika!

1438
01:18:53,329 --> 01:18:54,162
Hey, thanks.

1439
01:18:54,197 --> 01:18:56,364
[GROANING]

1440
01:19:01,070 --> 01:19:02,036
It's moving.

1441
01:19:09,078 --> 01:19:10,077
All right.

1442
01:19:10,113 --> 01:19:11,045
Yeah!

1443
01:19:26,095 --> 01:19:27,962
Excuse me.

1444
01:19:27,997 --> 01:19:29,397
You said your name
was Ash, right?

1445
01:19:29,432 --> 01:19:30,965
That's right.

1446
01:19:31,000 --> 01:19:33,334
I've been acting
like such a fool,

1447
01:19:33,369 --> 01:19:37,104
spending so long shutting
myself up in my lab.

1448
01:19:37,140 --> 01:19:43,077
That's why Alva had such an
easy time tricking me that way.

1449
01:19:43,112 --> 01:19:45,346
You know what I think?

1450
01:19:45,381 --> 01:19:49,050
You should head out on your
own journey with a Pokemon.

1451
01:19:49,085 --> 01:19:50,051
Huh?

1452
01:19:50,086 --> 01:19:51,052
Mm-hmm.

1453
01:19:51,087 --> 01:19:53,054
Pika te.

1454
01:19:53,089 --> 01:19:54,021
[CRASH]

1455
01:19:54,057 --> 01:19:55,022
[GASPS]

1456
01:20:05,134 --> 01:20:06,100
[CRASH]

1457
01:20:15,245 --> 01:20:17,211
[PANTING]

1458
01:20:21,484 --> 01:20:22,583
Volcanion?

1459
01:20:22,619 --> 01:20:27,154
Say, perhaps I should create
an explosion right here.

1460
01:20:27,190 --> 01:20:29,156
ASH: It is the center
of the fortress

1461
01:20:29,192 --> 01:20:31,058
so I do think it
would be effective.

1462
01:20:31,094 --> 01:20:33,427
But then you won't
be able to escape.

1463
01:20:33,463 --> 01:20:35,162
Vita vio.

1464
01:20:35,198 --> 01:20:37,198
Yeah, that's the truth.

1465
01:20:37,233 --> 01:20:40,334
You said you're powerful enough
to level a mountain, right?

1466
01:20:40,370 --> 01:20:43,137
So why not follow the plan
and blow it up from outside?

1467
01:20:43,172 --> 01:20:44,505
Hmm.

1468
01:20:44,541 --> 01:20:46,507
Agreed.

1469
01:20:46,543 --> 01:20:48,175
We should all go back together.

1470
01:20:48,211 --> 01:20:49,143
Yeah.

1471
01:20:49,178 --> 01:20:50,077
Pika!

1472
01:20:50,113 --> 01:20:52,079
[CRASH]

1473
01:20:52,115 --> 01:20:53,047
Let's hurry.

1474
01:21:00,256 --> 01:21:01,155
[CRASH]

1475
01:21:01,190 --> 01:21:02,156
[ALL GASP]

1476
01:21:15,505 --> 01:21:17,171
OK, Volcanion.

1477
01:21:17,206 --> 01:21:18,372
Go get them!

1478
01:21:18,408 --> 01:21:19,206
[GRUNTS]

1479
01:21:30,286 --> 01:21:32,219
Get on board after the blast.

1480
01:21:32,255 --> 01:21:34,021
All right.

1481
01:21:34,057 --> 01:21:35,356
Just go!

1482
01:21:35,391 --> 01:21:37,358
[ALL MOANING]

1483
01:21:41,431 --> 01:21:42,363
CHYMIA: Volcanion!

1484
01:21:48,404 --> 01:21:49,236
No!

1485
01:21:49,272 --> 01:21:51,038
You can't do that!

1486
01:21:56,279 --> 01:21:57,511
[GRUNTS]

1487
01:22:07,490 --> 01:22:10,458
Well, I'm going
out with a bang.

1488
01:22:10,493 --> 01:22:12,093
Time to blast!

1489
01:22:21,504 --> 01:22:26,173
Magearna, I couldn't
protect you.

1490
01:22:26,209 --> 01:22:28,142
Forgive me.

1491
01:22:28,177 --> 01:22:31,178
[ROARING]

1492
01:22:38,121 --> 01:22:39,253
Volcanion.

1493
01:22:39,288 --> 01:22:42,023
[HIGH PITCHED SOUND]

1494
01:22:48,164 --> 01:22:51,098
[EXPLOSION]

1495
01:23:10,453 --> 01:23:13,087
You lied to us.

1496
01:23:13,122 --> 01:23:16,090
You said we'd all
go back together!

1497
01:23:16,125 --> 01:23:17,258
Heego bego.

1498
01:23:41,150 --> 01:23:43,217
Magearna?

1499
01:23:43,252 --> 01:23:46,020
The Nebel Plateau
Pokemon are safe.

1500
01:23:46,055 --> 01:23:49,190
Volcanion protected them.

1501
01:23:49,225 --> 01:23:51,292
I wish you could
hear what I'm saying.

1502
01:23:51,327 --> 01:23:54,095
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1503
01:23:59,102 --> 01:24:01,068
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1504
01:24:04,307 --> 01:24:06,073
[PURRING]

1505
01:24:10,313 --> 01:24:12,079
[CRYING]

1506
01:24:12,115 --> 01:24:14,248
[GASPS]

1507
01:24:14,283 --> 01:24:17,051
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1508
01:24:20,289 --> 01:24:22,256
[GASPING]

1509
01:24:29,132 --> 01:24:30,097
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1510
01:24:30,133 --> 01:24:31,298
Look at the mist.

1511
01:24:31,334 --> 01:24:32,299
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1512
01:24:39,275 --> 01:24:40,241
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1513
01:24:49,085 --> 01:24:50,050
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1514
01:24:54,090 --> 01:24:55,055
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1515
01:25:14,110 --> 01:25:16,043
[BEEPING]

1516
01:25:20,049 --> 01:25:21,215
[GRUNTING]

1517
01:25:21,250 --> 01:25:23,217
[BEEPING]

1518
01:25:23,252 --> 01:25:25,219
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1519
01:25:26,222 --> 01:25:27,988
Magearna.

1520
01:25:28,024 --> 01:25:30,991
[BEEPING]

1521
01:25:37,166 --> 01:25:39,166
Chesnah.

1522
01:25:39,202 --> 01:25:40,134
Chesnah.

1523
01:25:44,340 --> 01:25:45,306
[GRUNTING]

1524
01:25:45,341 --> 01:25:47,308
[BEEPING]

1525
01:25:48,311 --> 01:25:50,077
[GRUNTS]

1526
01:25:52,114 --> 01:25:54,281
[GROANS]

1527
01:25:54,317 --> 01:25:57,251
[ALL GASP]

1528
01:25:57,286 --> 01:25:59,320
Volcanion, hang in there.

1529
01:26:01,290 --> 01:26:02,223
Volcanion?

1530
01:26:06,462 --> 01:26:08,095
Oh.

1531
01:26:08,130 --> 01:26:10,064
Pika.

1532
01:26:10,099 --> 01:26:13,000
[WHIMPERING]

1533
01:26:24,313 --> 01:26:25,212
[GASPS]

1534
01:26:25,248 --> 01:26:27,982
[SQUEAKING]

1535
01:26:28,017 --> 01:26:30,317
[GASPING]

1536
01:26:32,221 --> 01:26:34,054
[SNEEZES]

1537
01:26:34,090 --> 01:26:36,156
[POKEMON SCREAM]

1538
01:26:39,328 --> 01:26:41,462
I told you not to do that.

1539
01:26:41,497 --> 01:26:44,064
[POKEMON SQUEAKING]

1540
01:26:46,068 --> 01:26:49,136
You, you're still here?

1541
01:26:49,171 --> 01:26:52,239
I said I want to
protect Pokemon, right?

1542
01:26:52,275 --> 01:26:54,241
I would never tell a lie.

1543
01:26:54,277 --> 01:26:56,043
Be davi ya!

1544
01:26:56,078 --> 01:27:00,948
[CHUCKLES] All of you.

1545
01:27:00,983 --> 01:27:02,182
You know what?

1546
01:27:02,218 --> 01:27:04,118
Huh?

1547
01:27:04,153 --> 01:27:08,322
I'm going to make you all
honorary Nebel Plateau Pokemon.

1548
01:27:08,357 --> 01:27:10,190
Honorary Pokemon.

1549
01:27:10,226 --> 01:27:12,993
Hey, I think that
sounds really cool.

1550
01:27:13,029 --> 01:27:16,263
Yeah, I want to be one!

1551
01:27:16,299 --> 01:27:18,198
Yeah, right, Squishy?

1552
01:27:18,234 --> 01:27:19,366
Mm-hmm.

1553
01:27:19,402 --> 01:27:21,335
Well, I'm happy to accept.

1554
01:27:21,370 --> 01:27:23,003
It's a real honor.

1555
01:27:23,039 --> 01:27:24,371
[ALL LAUGHING]

1556
01:27:32,315 --> 01:27:34,281
Hey, electric nuisance.

1557
01:27:34,317 --> 01:27:35,382
Pika.

1558
01:27:35,418 --> 01:27:38,152
Your friend, Ash,
he always seems to be

1559
01:27:38,187 --> 01:27:40,220
getting himself into trouble.

1560
01:27:40,256 --> 01:27:41,355
Pika?

1561
01:27:41,390 --> 01:27:45,359
Take extra good care of him.

1562
01:27:45,394 --> 01:27:48,162
Pika, me gatsu.

1563
01:27:48,197 --> 01:27:49,396
[LAUGHS]

1564
01:28:10,186 --> 01:28:13,153
[MUSIC PLAYING]

1565
01:28:24,200 --> 01:28:27,201
WOMAN (SINGING):
One of a kind, forged

1566
01:28:27,236 --> 01:28:36,276
of steel from a beautiful
night with a mighty heart,

1567
01:28:36,312 --> 01:28:41,248
drove men apart.

1568
01:28:41,283 --> 01:28:48,422
Forgotten plain, where
only the damaged remain,

1569
01:28:48,457 --> 01:28:52,059
that's where I found my destiny.

1570
01:28:56,365 --> 01:29:05,406
One more lost refugee, come
with me, feel my soul-heart.

1571
01:29:05,441 --> 01:29:09,410
If you've been
seeking a new start,

1572
01:29:09,445 --> 01:29:18,419
let me be your guiding light
till the end of the night.

1573
01:29:18,454 --> 01:29:23,090
Close your eyes,
know my soul-heart,

1574
01:29:23,125 --> 01:29:27,127
keeping watch over the rampart.

1575
01:29:27,163 --> 01:29:33,133
Let me be your
shining star, leading

1576
01:29:33,169 --> 01:29:41,241
voice from afar from whoever
you were to whoever you are.

1577
01:29:44,213 --> 01:29:48,115
Feel my soul-heart now.

1578
01:29:51,320 --> 01:29:54,088
Dry all your tears.

1579
01:29:54,123 --> 01:29:59,393
I've returned after so many
years Let the creatures

1580
01:29:59,428 --> 01:30:04,364
I cherish flourish so now.

1581
01:30:07,403 --> 01:30:11,138
This is my vow.

1582
01:30:11,173 --> 01:30:15,275
Know forever my soul-heart.

1583
01:30:15,311 --> 01:30:24,318
Anyone seeking a new start,
let me be your guiding light

1584
01:30:24,353 --> 01:30:29,423
till the end of the night.

1585
01:30:29,458 --> 01:30:31,425
(GUITAR SOLO)

1586
